10 delicious sandwiches with red fish that will disappear from the table first
05 Nov 2019, 05:00 by Irina Sakharova
Interesting and simple snacks with avocados, curd cheese, olives, eggs and more.
Lightly salted, smoked or smoked salmon, trout, pink salmon and chum salmon are great for these dishes.
1. Sandwiches with red fish, butter and lemon



AndreySt / Depositphotos.com


Ingredients

1 seedless olive;
1 slice of lemon;
2 slices of bread;
1 teaspoon butter;
2 slices of red fish;
1 sprig of dill.

Cooking
Cut the olive and lemon slice into halves.
Spread the bread with butter. Put a lemon on top. Roll fish pieces into a ‚Äúrose‚Äù and secure the edge with a skewer on which the olive is strung. Garnish with dill.
