2. Sandwiches with red fish, cucumber and curd cheese


Warburtons.co.uk

Ingredients

1 cucumber;
2 slices of bread;
1 tablespoon of curd cheese;
2 slices of smoked red fish;
pepper - to taste;
a few leaves of arugula.

Cooking
Cut two long thin slices from a cucumber using a mandolin grater or a regular peeler.
Slices of bread with curd cheese. Put cucumber and fish on top. Sprinkle with pepper and garnish with arugula.
