3. Sandwich with red fish, avocado, tomatoes and onions


Seriouseats.com

Ingredients

1 slice of bread;
¬Ω teaspoon of olive oil;
¬Ω avocado;
¬Ω lemon;
1 tablespoon of soft goat cheese;
2 slices of tomato;
2-3 onion half rings;
2-3 slices of red fish;
salt and pepper to taste.

Cooking
Brown bread in a couple of minutes with butter over medium heat. Cool a little. Mash avocados with a fork to make a paste. Squeeze the juice from the lemon.
Grease a slice of cheese, top with avocados, tomatoes, onions and fish. Pour in lemon juice. Salt and pepper.
