5. Sandwiches with red fish, curd cheese and pesto



La_vanda / Depositphotos.com


Ingredients

2 slices of bread;
3 tablespoons of curd cheese;
2 tablespoons pesto;
2 slices of red fish;
a few leaves of basil or other herbs.

Cooking
Grease the bread with cottage cheese, and then pesto. Put red fish on top and garnish with basil.
