6. Sandwiches with red fish, cottage cheese and olives



teresaterra / Depositphotos.com


Ingredients

2-3 olives;
1-2 cherry tomatoes;
4 slices of bread;
5-6 tablespoons of cottage cheese;
4 pieces of red fish;
1 sprig of parsley.

Cooking
Cut olives and cherry into small pieces.
Slices of bread with half the cheese. Wrap the pieces of fish in tubes and add the cheese with olives and tomatoes inside. Put on bread and garnish with parsley.
