7. Sandwiches with red fish, carrots and capers


Delish.com

Ingredients

¬Ω carrots;
1 stalk of celery;
1-2 stalks of green onions;
3-4 tablespoons of cottage cheese;
1-2 tablespoons of capers;
1 tablespoon of lemon juice;
1 teaspoon of lemon zest;
4 slices of bread;
150 g of red fish;
1 sprig of dill.

Cooking
Grate carrots on a medium or fine grater. Grind celery. Chop green onions. Mix cheese with carrots, celery, capers, onions, lemon juice and zest.
Cut the slices of bread into halves and spread with the cheese mixture. Put fish on top and garnish with dill.
