9. Sandwich with red fish, avocado and brie cheese


Goodtoknow.co.uk

Ingredients

¬Ω avocado;
30-50 g brie cheese;
2 slices of bread;
1 teaspoon butter;
50 g of red fish;
1 slice of lemon;
¬Ω teaspoon poppy seeds;
pepper to taste.

Cooking
Slice the avocado, crumble the cheese.
Grease one slice of bread with butter. Place fish with avocado on top. Sprinkle juice with a slice of lemon. Put brie on top, sprinkle with poppy seeds and black pepper. Cover with a second piece of bread or serve a sandwich without it.
